node.accessibility_caption: Photo by ξνεrτ : on December 23, 2019. Geen fotobeschrijving beschikbaar.

node.text:
Vintage 1910 Neufeldt & Kuhnke Kiel headphone restoration complete. Project took me a month to complete. No hurry just hobby and fooling around 🤫 first time I did this and I think it came out nicely. Used an old belt of my grandfather, rest his soul... .
Using his belt gave it a personal touch I like and I think he would have liked it too. The original headband was moldy and the headphone itself was very rusty. With a little vinegar and Brasso the metal started to come alive again.
.
Nice project, I had a lot of fun ❤
.
.
.
.
.
